[WSAD] - Camera movement
[MOUSE WHEEL] - Camera zoom

(PAUSE - YELLOW):

  [SPACE] - Start simulation
  [ENTER] - Add Planet   
  [CLICK ON PLANET] - Edit planet
   
(EDITOR - RED):
  
  [C] - Make "carousel"
    [+] - Add orbiter
    [-] - Remove one orbiter   
  [V] - Set velocity  
  [P] - Set position  
  [O] - Make orbiter
    [+] - Make orbit longer
    [-] - Make orbit shorter    
  [R] - Set radius (and mass)  
  [BACKSPACE] - Remove planet
  [CLICK OUTSIDE PLANET | ENTER] - End editing
    
  (EDITOR - RED):
  
  [SPACE] - Pause simulation
  [CLICK ON PLANET] - Follow planet
  [E] - Follow next planet
  [Q] - Follow previous planet  
